:00 UTC using the time-weighted average premium between perpetual and spot prices. The exchange applies a dampening mechanism when rates exceed ±0.75% to prevent extreme funding costs. Portfolio margin mode allows efficient capital utilization across BLUR positions and other crypto assets. Funding settlements occur automatically without requiring manual intervention."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
